Definition: a formal entry into an organization or position or office
Example: his initiation into the club; he was ordered to report for induction into the army; he gave a speech as part of his installation into the hall of fame
Synonyms: verb, social, initiate, induction, induct, installation, install, ceremony, a, formal, entry, into, an, organization, or, position, office, his, the, club, he, was, ordered, to, report, for, army, gave, speech, as, part, of, hall, fame
Category: noun.event
